song.title: 72. Nightscape Fencing (within a Space Temple of Contra Sidescrollers)
song.info: Boy has this song been lying around for a long time. This is one of the first songs I made for renoise. I've never been quite happy with it. So now when I recently installed a few new vsti's I decided to finish it up. Once done the song had the same title as it had a year ago. "New Template". So I sent the song to a few friends and asked if they could come up with a neat songname for me. Here's the results: "Temple of ...", "Contra Sidescroller Level from 1993", "Nightscape Fencing" So I decided to mash it up a bit, and well, yeah that's it. :) Thanx to: "Tatsujin, cgmonkey & Metal-Ridley" for coming up with the name. Thanx to: "overcoat" for making me adjust some notes Oh and thanx to: maep, prowler & fishboy876 for making this possible
